body:
over 2 months a go i got permabanned for behavior. &lt;br&gt;
since that day i keept thinking on what i did and why it was that toxic. i really didnt know the gravity of what i said , i was simple joking with a friend and meaning to make fun in the lobby but i has been annoying in chat.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
i love this game and enjoyed it so much, i supported you as well cuz i think you make a good job on features and on behavior of players (except for inting which sadly still in the game) .i know a player that got unbanned from permaban and he said things like &quot;kys&quot; &quot;pleb&quot; and so on.i always has been a competitive player,never surrended and never told someone to kill them self or similar.i said a bad racism word on purpuose of make fun but using the forum i noticed how much bad that word is.i also noticed that &quot;gj&quot; and &quot;gg easy&quot; are considered negative words by the system.i also forgot caps lock on sometimes i think system misunderstood some of my meanings. im not saying i didnt flame, and im not saying i dont deserve a ban/limitation, im only saying that permanent one may its too much,and if you think 14 days isnt enought, well i passed 2 months thinking on what i done looking my chat log.i just typed too much but thats because im fast, i still paying while typing&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
my friend made fun of me, i didnt enjoy all your events missions and new skins, i has been over 2 months in the little corner of the room thinking on what i done.i cant believe you think stay in this forever would resolve the problem,but somehow it did but i wanna prove that by showing you my reform.i know you probably asking me to make a new account, well 3 ppl already gave me them account lv 100 with over 30 skins, but its not the same thing, i dont like to lie , as i did with you i always tell what i think and ask to resolve problems.but i learned the lesson , i dont have to use chat anymore &lt;br&gt;
even if i think thats a big waste,ill never use chat again since even if you say gj 5 times u being annoying in chat. ima really changed person i changed way to think and way to play. but create an account isnt possible for me, i really get depressed everytime i play league since that day its literally like im IP-banned.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
as i said,i didnt know the gravity of what i said and i just wanted to make a laugh with some friends, but i miserably failed. &lt;br&gt;
so,im there pleasing you to forgive me.pls riot review this:&lt;br&gt;
