as i said,im not feeling unfair-banned and im not playing the role of the bulled boy saying everyone target me,i know i did wrong and i deserved a ban/limitation&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
the 2 week ban was on 20 of june and i really believed to be reformed and i didnt believe system could permaban me after i reached honor lv 1. &lt;br&gt;
im not trying to justify me and im not saying every player would have do that, i know i didnt have to use chat (even if i think its a waste keep ppl flaming on chat without try let them think on what they are doing)and simple mute all.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
as i said im not saying the ban system do not work well, im only saying in that case some of my phrase could get misunderstood and (as some players told me ) 14 days ban was enought. &lt;br&gt;
NOW i know that even if i feel offended i have to mute all and dont reply (even if i hate stay with hands in my hands and wait to someone help me, it just let me feel weak i got bullying problems in the past and after lessons i learned that i have to reply if dont want the other to put them feet on my head. but NOW i&amp;apos;ll just do what riot ask me and even if i think thats the wrong way ,i&amp;apos;ll do it )&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
i know league is a free-to-play game,and (as i can see) im not forcing you to give me my account back ,im simple saying since i supported you by calling my friends (that actually spent 600 &euro; on this game) and supported you as well with my money and since i tried to do what riot forum should me to do , i never surrended and never stopped playing trying to go on without get tilt.im saying, since i supported you very well,why arent you collaborating with me&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
i feel im reformed but, create a new account it does not make sense let me explain why (yeah im talking like a rioter sry for this belief,but i hope this can help you on making a new permaban mechanics,):&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
-making a new account does not give me back my skins, my friends list,my mastery points but most importantly nobody will ever care about check my reform, i mean even reaching honor 5 i wont get riot congratulations or any reward related to my old account. for example &lt;br&gt;
if making a new account and reaching honor 5 could get my account back, i would immediately go play league again .same if i could get back my money/skins on the new account .&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
this is what would engage ppl to reform .meanwhile knowing i cant get back my account just make me feel bad ,unistall league,and go play another game&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
another reason of why im not making a new account is: &lt;br&gt;
making a new account every ppl i meet make fun of me (and reading to your private policy thats not exactly what you want right?)even my friends i called on this game made fun of me (and considerating they tilt every game i dont get why they are honor 5, the only thing they do is to make fun of EVERY player they meet and tilt when they die, but since they are honor 5 i think thats exactly what riot want them to do)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
another reason is: since its always me playing, where is the meaning of dont giv eme my account back, it still me playing the only thing that change is the angry of playing without old stuff (which mean more flammers will born instead of new reformed guys)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
you dont have to sorry, im not upset to you but theres one thing you can do sent this to the player behavior specialist so they can review this.and as i said i know what i did wrong,im happy you used your time to explain me , but i already knew.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
i hope i explained myself&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Thank in advice for listening
